## Interface: 120007
## Title: LibCodex-1.0-Battlemasters
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / Battlemasters (Experimental PTR flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the Battlemasters module. Per-module split keeps the core lib's bytecode pool tiny and lets consumers pay only for modules they query.
