# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# Battlemasters catalog for the Experimental PTR flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against Battlemasters.

Data_XPTR\Battlemasters.lua
